<BaseLayout
  title="Start Here"
  description="New to personal finance? Start here. No experience required."
>
  <h1>Start Here</h1>

  <p>BeginnerFinanceHub exists for one reason: to make personal finance feel less overwhelming. Not through hacks or shortcuts, but through clear, honest explanations that meet you where you are. Every piece of content here is written with a specific reader in mind -- someone who wants to get a handle on their money but isn't sure how to begin.</p>

  <p>You don't need any background in finance to be here. If you've ever avoided opening your bank app, felt embarrassed not knowing what a term means, or kept meaning to sort things out but never quite started -- this is for you. Topics here are chosen because they come up in real life, not because they look good on a syllabus.</p>

  <p>The best place to start is wherever you feel most stuck. If you're not sure, try the <a href="/articles">first article on tracking your spending</a>. You don't need to do everything at once. One small step is enough.</p>
</BaseLayout>
